p.k: Claudio Iturra (conductor) part to Kenya to go into the Massai Mara National Park, one of the most beautiful nature reserves of Planet Earth. However, part of their journey in order to reach the Mara River, from inside the Massai Mara, home to hippos, lions and the great Nile Crocodile, main objectives of the team in this new adventure.
